node.text:
Follow @the.frenchdiver for more. Metamorphosis 🐸 🤯 🌍 

The process in which a tadpole turns into a frog is called metamorphosis, and it is an amazing transformation. Here @victorharold have broken metamorphosis down so you can see the stages a tadpole goes through as it develops into an adult.

Have you ever witness this in real life? 
📽 @victorharold

Which of these colorful birds is your favorite? 😍 Share your photos with us and we will post them in our account. Apply for a feature following the link in our bio: @wanderfervor 

From 1 to 10? 🦜🎨

Names and Photos: 
1. Silver throated Tanager @jeffreypatrickkarnes
2. European Starling @raheel.aazim
3. Mandarin duck @eccentricwildlife
4. Golden-tailed Sapphire @birddetective
5. Strawberry Finch @praharsha_wildlife_stories
6. Periquito-rico @macrotake
7. European Bee-eater @dorugroza
8. Pink Robin @ravi_arora
9. Keel billed Toucan @floriankusterwildlife
10. Oriental Dwarf Kingfisher @rahul_belsare
